rComments: Bruce is really a nice person. He is knowledgeable, really interested in the material and so caring. Unfortunately he is retiring but in case he would offer other courses I would definitely go for it!
Don't sit up front because if he learns your name, he'll nail you for skipping lectures. Very clear though, you just have to listen and pay attn.
